# SASS Installation Steps

1. Installed Node Version Manager (NVM):
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

2. Restarted terminal:
   exit
   (Then reopened terminal)

3. Installed Node.js version 20.16 using NVM:
   nvm install 20.16
   nvm use 20.16

4. Verified node and npm versions:
   node -v
   npm -v

5. Installed SASS globally using npm:
   npm install -g sass@3.7.4

6. Verified SASS installation:
   sass --version
